         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 24th October. 1887. ¶ I feel justified to attest that I found Mr. F. W. Reichelt's 'Dandelion Ale' to be a light, refreshing and palatable beverage, free from any unwholesome ingredients, a...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.10.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Testimonial</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The text given here is from an advertisement in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>, 19 November 1892, p. 14: </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.1665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: -0.5in; "
                     xml:lang="en">…</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.1665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: -0.5in; "
                     xml:lang="en">REMEDY FOR LIVER COMPLAINT. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.1665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: -0.5in; "
                     xml:lang="en">The latest, healthiest most pleasant Drink. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.1665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: -0.5in; "
                     xml:lang="en">REICHELT'S DANDELION ALE, DANDELION PORTER, </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.1665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: -0.5in; "
                     xml:lang="en">REICHELT'S GERMAN WEISSBEER, Non-intoxicating. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Especially brewed for this climate, wholesome, refreshing for family use. No mother in want of nourishment ought to be without it.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">…</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">After listing places where it is available, M's testimonial is printed, and followed by</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Analysed and highly recommended by </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6665in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">C. R. BLACKETT, Government Analyst</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 1.5in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                     </seg>JOHN KRUSE. Analyst</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's name was used in advertisements for the beverage from at least 1889 until 1894, although often not with the full text given here. Later advertisements carried testimonials from additional supporters. </p>
               </note>Melbourne, 24th October. 1887.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I feel justified to attest that I found Mr. F. W. Reichelt's 'Dandelion Ale' to be a light, refreshing and palatable beverage, free from any unwholesome ingredients, and particularly calculated to stimulate digestion and promote nutrition.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">BARON VON MUELLER, M &amp; Ph.</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>D <seg style="font-style: italic; ">omitted</seg>?</p>
               </note>
               <seg style="">, F.C.S.</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Fellow of the Chemical Society, to which M was elected in 1884.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
